Package: GammaGateR
Type: Package
Title: Marker Gating for Cell-level Multiplexed Immunofluorescence Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: @R: c(
    person("Jiangmei", "Xiong", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    email = "jiangmei.xiong@vanderbilt.edu"),
    person("Simon", "Vandekar", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "simon.vandekar@vumc.org")
    )
Maintainer: Jiangmei Xiong <jiangmei.xiong@vanderbilt.edu>
Description: This package uses Gamma Mixture Model to semi-automate the marker gating process.    Interactive scatter plot and fitted model density curves can be generated as a reference for goodness of fit.    Adjusted rand index can be generated to compare marker gating result with manual label silver standard, if available.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Collate:
    'GammaGateR.R'
    'histograms.R'
    'monoZ.R'
    'groupGammaGateR.R'
    'diag.R'
